<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Werewolf Skin Cloak Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Kill a werewolf for their skin.<BR>
<BR>
2) Find and hail Karg Icebear in Everfrost.  Give Karg 100pp and the werewolf skin and you will recieve a Werewolf Skin Cloak.</div>
<BR>
