<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have now done this quest twice- the skin is an ultra rare drop, and to make things worse, it can be quite difficult to find Karg- if you do find find him immediately he is killed by another player.<BR>
<BR>
This item is a rare one and can fetch 800p to 1000p at the sunday bazaar. Thus item as stated before is excelent for a monk.<BR>
<BR>
An interesting thing about the werewolf cloak... be extremely careful not to ever drop this item on the ground. It has a tendency to go poof on you. I have confirmed 3 instances of this happening, one was my own and did not realize what happened until hearing about the other 2 times.</font></td></tr></table>
